item.name: Netherlands
item.title: Anne Frank House, Netherlands
item.dec: The Anne Frank House is a must-see when in Amsterdam. On Prinsengracht, in the home where Anne's family hid for much of WWII

item.name: Brazil
item.title: Rio de Janeiro, Brazil
item.dec: Rio's first settlement began below these peaks, near the long Praia da Urca beach, and you can tour one of the three early forts there, the star-shaped Fort São João.
